          <p class='first-para'>
            I want to ask a simple-minded question. Does the clause as drafted give more priority to the board than the trustees would anyway have?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-03021'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040907_GCR_133'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
